 "remarks": "Welcome to this spacious, sun-drenched corner unit located in the pristine Strawberry Hill neighborhood at Regency Towers. This beautifully maintained condo features two generously sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms, complemented by an open-concept living and dining area that flows seamlessly into the kitchen-perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. Large windows fill the home with natural light and offer beautiful views, while the private balcony off the living room-recently refinished and upgraded with brand-new mosquito screen enclosures-provides the perfect setting to relax and enjoy spectacular sunsets.  Additional highlights include a reserved parking space in the underground garage and Laundry on each floor. Residents of Regency Towers benefit from exceptional amenities, including an on-site superintendent, professional door staff, and an upgraded security system for added peace of mind.  The HOA conveniently includes heat, hot water, and cooking gas, making this home as practical as it is inviting.",
